WEBVTT

00:03.462 --> 00:06.172
4:22 on
a sunny Thursday afternoon here...

00:06.382 --> 00:08.007
...in Chicago, on K-LITE.

00:08.217 --> 00:10.927
Now, here's one for all you
rush-hour rockers.

00:11.136 --> 00:14.555
The Beach Boys with "Good Vibrations."

00:16.000 --> 00:22.074
